# Keystore files — NEVER commit these.
# The release key signs published APKs; exposure means anyone can publish
# updates that impersonate this app.  Rotate immediately if accidentally committed.
# Store credentials in local.properties (also gitignored above):
#   KEYSTORE_PASSWORD=...
#   KEY_ALIAS=release
#   KEY_PASSWORD=...
*.jks
*.keystore
